  "metadata": {
    "role": "article",
    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Including notes for testers with a beta release of your app"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can include notes when you distribute a beta version of your app from Xcode Cloud through TestFlight",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to give testers details about the changes the update includes, and to provide guidance for",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the areas of your app to test. Use these notes to focus testing on the areas of your",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "app that need attention. The notes appear in the “What to test” field in the TestFlight",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "app. The information you provide can be language- and locale-specific.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information about distributing a beta version of your app, see",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Creating-a-workflow-that-builds-your-app-for-distribution",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Session 10224: ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023/10224",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Related sessions from WWDC23",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Create-a-TestFlight-folder",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Create a TestFlight folder",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Xcode Cloud uses text files that you add to your Xcode project to create the notes for testers. The text files",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "reside in a folder named TestFlight located in the same folder as your Xcode project or workspace.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To create the TestFlight folder:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Open your project or workspace in Xcode.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the Project navigator, Control-click your project and choose New Group to create the group and its corresponding folder.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Name the new group TestFlight.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-text-files-to-the-folder-to-include-notes",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add text files to the folder to include notes",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Add text files to the TestFlight folder to provide notes to your testers. Provide notes in multiple languages by creating a file per language. For a list of the locales TestFlight supports, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/AppStoreConnectAPI/BetaBuildLocalizationCreateRequest/Data-data.dictionary/Attributes-data.dictionary",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For general information on language and region codes, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/choosing-localization-regions-and-scripts",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add the text files to your project:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Add a new Empty file to the TestFlight folder. For instructions, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/managing-files-and-folders-in-your-xcode-project",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Name the file using the format ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "WhatToTest.<LOCALE>.txt",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". For",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "LOCALE",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", use the language and region code for the content you provide in the file. For example, use ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "WhatToTest.en-US.txt",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " for U.S. English.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Commit and push the file to your remote repository.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The next time Xcode Cloud builds and uploads your app to TestFlight, it automatically",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "finds this file and includes the text in your app’s “What to test” field in TestFlight.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Provide-useful-and-appropriate-content",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Provide useful and appropriate content",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Include information that is useful to testers and relevant to the current release, such as the following:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Features you add to your app.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Issues you resolve in your code.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The commit message for the commit that triggers the build, or the past few commit messages.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "When Xcode Cloud deploys your app, the information you provide is available",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "to all testers in all groups who have access to the build.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Write-a-script-to-generate-content-dynamically",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Write a script to generate content dynamically",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can use a custom build script to generate the notes during an Xcode Cloud build. The following example provides the last three commit messages from the GIT log as the tester notes:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "#!/bin/zsh",
            "#  ci_post_xcodebuild.sh",
            "",
            "if [[ -d \"$CI_APP_STORE_SIGNED_APP_PATH\" ]]; then",
            "  TESTFLIGHT_DIR_PATH=../TestFlight",
            "  mkdir $TESTFLIGHT_DIR_PATH",
            "  git fetch --deepen 3 && git log -3 --pretty=format:\"%s\" >! $TESTFLIGHT_DIR_PATH/WhatToTest.en-US.txt",
            "fi"
          ],
          "syntax": null,
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Writing-Custom-Build-Scripts",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
